name: Empire of the Ants
description:
The design of the empire of ants goes back to my childhood fantasies when I followed a group of ants from their collecting food and accompanied them as much as possible. As far as they could enter the closed gates of their city, their existence is so far from human eyes. It was there that the rest of the city was built in my mind. Here I have reconstructed some of those fantasies.

MUSIC:CUCUVOXELART
SIZE:1500*1200
